trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming i en visuelle utformeren for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control is used as a container for other controls, especially when controls are generated programmatically.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontrollen skal brukes som en beholder for andre kontroller spesielt når Kontroller genereres programmatisk.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>

trans-unit.source: In a visual designer, when you switch from Source to Design view, the markup source code that describes the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control is parsed, and a design-time version of the control is created on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: I en visuelle utformeren når du bytter fra kilden til utformingsvisning koden kildekode som beskriver de tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontrollen analysert, og en utformingen versjon av kontrollen opprettes på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>

trans-unit.source: When you switch back to Source view, the design-time control is persisted to markup source code and edited into the markup for the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Når du går tilbake til visning i datakilden, er utformingen kontrollen beholdt i markup kildekode og redigeres i markup for websiden.

trans-unit.source: The PanelContainerDesigner class provides design-time support for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> controls in a visual designer.
trans-unit.target: Klassen PanelContainerDesigner gir støtte for utforming for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>Kontroller i en visuelle utformeren.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.FrameCaption%2A> property gets the caption that appears on the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.FrameCaption%2A>egenskapen henter teksten som vises for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.FrameCaption%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.FrameStyle%2A> property gets the styles of the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.FrameStyle%2A>egenskapen henter stilen for den tilknyttede kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.FrameStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> property always returns `true`, indicating that the designer creates a temporary copy of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>egenskapen returnerer alltid `true`, som angir at det opprettes en midlertidig kopi av det tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>til å generere utformingen markup.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.Initialize%2A> method prepares the designer to view, edit, and design the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.Initialize%2A>metoden Klargjør utformeren for å vise, redigere og utforme den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.Initialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.AddDesignTimeCssAttributes%2A> method sets collection elements to the string representations of various style attributes of the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.AddDesignTimeCssAttributes%2A>metoden angir Samlingselementer til streng gjengivelsene av forskjellige Stilattributter for den tilknyttede kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.AddDesignTimeCssAttributes%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner> class when it creates the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control or a copy of that control on the visual designer surface.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt bygger en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner>klasse når det oppretter den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontroll eller en kopi av denne kontrollen i visual utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Adds string representations of style attributes to a collection to be used in the design-time rendering of the control.
trans-unit.target: Legger til av Stilattributter i en samling som skal brukes i utformingen gjengivelse av kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The AddDesignTimeCssAttributes method calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ContainerControlDesigner.AddDesignTimeCssAttributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName> base method, which adds string representations of style attributes to the `styleAttributes` collection.
trans-unit.target: Metodekall AddDesignTimeCssAttributes den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ContainerControlDesigner.AddDesignTimeCssAttributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName>basere metode, som legger til av Stilattributter i `styleAttributes` samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ContainerControlDesigner.AddDesignTimeCssAttributes%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: These attributes are based on the style properties of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control.
trans-unit.target: Disse attributtene er basert på egenskapene stilen for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>

trans-unit.source: The AddDesignTimeCssAttributes sets the direction of `styleAttribute` to a code indicating left-to-right or right-to-left, based on the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.Direction%2A> property of the associated control.
trans-unit.target: AddDesignTimeCssAttributes angir retningen på `styleAttribute` til en kode som angir venstre mot høyre eller fra høyre mot venstre, basert på verdien for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.Direction%2A>for den tilknyttede kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.Direction%2A>

trans-unit.source: A collection of style attributes implementing the <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>.
trans-unit.target: En samling av Stilattributter implementere <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>.</xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>

trans-unit.source: Gets the caption that appears on the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter teksten som vises for den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The FrameCaption property returns the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.GroupingText%2A> property of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer de FrameCaption den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.GroupingText%2A>for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel.GroupingText%2A>

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the panel caption.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder teksten panelet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the styles of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter stilen for den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.FrameCaption%2A> property is an empty string (""), the FrameStyle property returns an empty <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style> object.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.FrameCaption%2A>egenskapen er en tom streng (""), FrameStyle returneres en tom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.PanelContainerDesigner.FrameCaption%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the FrameStyle property returns a default <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style> object that is generated by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ContainerControlDesigner.FrameStyle%2A?displayProperty=fullName> base property.
trans-unit.target: Ellers egenskapen FrameStyle Returnerer standard <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>objektet som er generert av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ContainerControlDesigner.FrameStyle%2A?displayProperty=fullName>basere egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ContainerControlDesigner.FrameStyle%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"></xref> object that contains the design-time styles for the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Style"> </xref> objekt som inneholder utformingen stiler for den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Prepares the designer to view, edit, and design the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Forbereder utformeren for å vise, redigere og utforme den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The visual designer calls the Initialize method when it is ready to use the designer to render the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control.
trans-unit.target: Den visuelle utformeren kaller i initialiseringsmetoden når den er klar til å bruke designer til å gjengi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>

trans-unit.source: The Initialize and its base methods configure properties and set up events that are necessary for the operation of the designer.
trans-unit.target: Initialiseringen og tilhørende base metoder Konfigurer egenskaper og hendelser som er nødvendige for operasjonen av designer.

trans-unit.source: The `component` parameter is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control that is associated with this designer or a copy of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control.
trans-unit.target: Den `component` parameteren er av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontrollen som er tilknyttet utformeren eller en kopi av det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel"></xref>, which implements an <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel"> </xref>, som implementerer en <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: component is not a or of a class derived from .
trans-unit.target: componenter ikke en eller av en klasse som er avledet fra .

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the designer should use a temporary copy rather than the actual control that is associated with the designer to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om designer må bruke en midlertidig kopi i stedet for den faktiske kontrollen som er forbundet med designer for å generere utformingen markup.

trans-unit.source: Because the UsePreviewControl property is always `true`, the designer uses a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control that contains a copy of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> control to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Fordi egenskapen UsePreviewControl alltid `true`, designer bruker en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>kontroll som inneholder en kopi av det tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>kontrollen til å generere utformingen markup.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control does not affect any persistence for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>Kontrollen påvirker ikke noen utholdenhet for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>

trans-unit.source: If the UsePreviewControl property has been overridden to return `false`, the designer will use the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel> itself to generate the design-time markup, and design-time changes to the control will persist to the page markup source.
trans-unit.target: Hvis egenskapen UsePreviewControl er overstyrt for å returnere `false`, designer bruker den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>selve å generere utformingen markup, og endre utformingen kontrollen vil beholde siden markup kilde.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Panel>
